{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Web 图形开发","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Guide/Graphics","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>现代网站和应用需要呈现大量图片。展示静态签 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a>，也可以采用 CSS 样式中的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/background-image\"><code>background-image</code></a> 属性。与此同时，你也能绘制出动态图像，或者是对图像进行巧妙处理。这些文章可以帮助你了解如何做到这些事情。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"2d_图像","title":"2D 图像","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"canvas\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a>提供了一些使用 JavaScript 来绘制 2D 图像的接口</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"svg\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG\">SVG</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>可缩放矢量图形 (SVG) 帮助你使用直线，曲线，和其他的几何图形来生成（渲染）图像。通过使用矢量图形，你能够画出任意拉伸也不失真的图像。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/tag/Graphics\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">查看全部...</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"3d_图像","title":"3D 图像","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"webgl\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API\">WebGL</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>开启 WebGL（即 Web 3D 图像 API）历程的指南。这项技术可帮助你在 Web 内容中使用标准的 OpenGL ES。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"视频","title":"视频","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"使用_html5_音频（audio）和_视频（video）\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Multimedia_and_embedding/Video_and_audio_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">使用 HTML5 音频（audio）和 视频（video） (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>在网页中嵌入视频/音频并控制其播放。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"webrtc\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebRTC_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">WebRTC (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>WebRTC 中的 RTC 代表实时通讯技术，这一技术允许音频/视频数据流在对等的浏览器客户端之间共享。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"2D 图像","id":"2d_图像"},{"text":"3D 图像","id":"3d_图像"},{"text":"视频","id":"视频"}],"summary":"现代网站和应用需要呈现大量图片。展示静态签 <img>，也可以采用 CSS 样式中的 background-image 属性。与此同时，你也能绘制出动态图像，或者是对图像进行巧妙处理。这些文章可以帮助你了解如何做到这些事情。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Graphics on the Web","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Gráficas en la web","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Graphismes sur le Web","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ウェブのグラフィック","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"웹 상 그래픽","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Gráficos na Web","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Графика для Web","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"網頁上的圖像","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/guide/graphics","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/guide/graphics/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Guide","title":"Web 开发者指南"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Guide/Graphics","title":"Web 图形开发"}],"pageTitle":"Web 图形开发 - Web 开发者指南 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}